### Get All Cards
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Request Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/request
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "cardType": "DEBIT"
}

### Get Card
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Activate Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/activate
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cvv": "123",
  "pin": "1234"
}

### Block Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/block?reason=Lost
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Unblock Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/unblock
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Change Pin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/change-pin
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPin": "1234",
  "newPin": "4321",
  "confirmPin": "4321"
}

### Replace Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/replace?reason=Damaged
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Report Lost Card
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/report-lost
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Cancel Card
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Limits
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/limits
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Set Card Limits
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/limits
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dailyLimit": 1000,
  "monthlyLimit": 5000,
  "atmLimit": 500,
  "posLimit": 2000
}

### Toggle Online Transactions
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/online-transactions?enabled=true
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Toggle Contactless
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/contactless?enabled=true
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Toggle International
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/international?enabled=true
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Transactions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/transactions?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Statement
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/statement?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/1/details
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Types
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/types
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Card Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/statistics
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cards/health
